Target Performance Budget:
  Vision processing (FIFO result): 20-30ms (from Phase 0)
  + ROS message overhead: 5ms
  + Python processing overhead: 5-10ms
  + RPi scheduling jitter: 5ms
  ─────────────────────────────────────
  Camera→cmd_vel latency: 35-50ms ✓
  
  + Motor actuation (MAVLink + servo): 10-15ms
  ─────────────────────────────────────
  Total end-to-end latency: 45-65ms ✓ (meets <100ms requirement)

If ROS latency exceeds FIFO baseline + 30ms, indicates ROS/Python bottleneck


Critical Metrics to Monitor:
----------------------------
1. Vision Processing Latency: camera timestamp → /cmd_vel publish
   - Target: <50ms mean, <70ms max
   - Measures: Image processing efficiency

2. Motor Actuation Latency: /cmd_vel timestamp → IMU change detection
   - Target: <20ms mean
   - Measures: MAVLink + ArduPilot + servo response

3. End-to-End Latency: camera capture → motor actuation
   - Target: <100ms total (for line following at 1 m/s)
   - Measures: Complete control loop performance

4. Jitter: Variance in latencies
   - Target: Coefficient of variation <15%
   - Measures: System determinism

5. Deadline Misses: Frames exceeding latency thresholds
   - Target: <5% miss rate
   - Measures: Real-time guarantee


